1. To change the actual functionality of perks, go to BP_BaseCharacter -> Apply Selected Perk Function
Then if you want to add a new perk, make sure to add a new execution pin for the switch node in Apply Selected Perk Function.
Then goto WB_CharacterSelection -> On Construct event to add the new perk.

2. In addition to #1 above, also add the name of the new perk to the EPerks enum obviously.

